title: Slow Cooker Chicken Tortilla Soup
description: This ultra-flavorful soup is worth the wait. The slow cooker makes it easy, and the savory combination of chicken, beans, corn and picante sauce makes it absolutely delicious!

title: Slow Cooker Hearty Beef Stew
description: Colorful, hearty and tender, this slow-cooked stew features all the traditional ingredients of a good beef stew: beef, carrots, onion, potatoes, peas in a rich gravy.

title: Loaded Potato Soup
description: Everything you love about loaded baked potatoes can be found in a bowl of this homemade soup that everyone will enjoy. It's rich and creamy, and full of great flavor that is sure to make this soup a cold weather favorite!

title: Slow Cooker Bacon Potato Chowder
description: This hearty and flavorful soup is so easy to make. Simply mix the ingredients in a slow cooker and let it do the work for you. And to make it even better, stir in Cheddar just before serving and top with a sprinkle of chives.

title: Sensational Chicken Noodle Soup
description: Sometimes you just want a good, old-fashioned chicken noodle soup. No fancy ingredients. Just great flavor.  Give this version a try. All you need is 6 ingredients and 35 minutes to make a home-style soup that you'll really enjoy.

title: White Chicken Chili
description: Campbell's Condensed Cream of Chicken Soup and dry onion soup and recipe mix combine to flavor this scrumptious chili featuring chicken, white kidney beans and chili powder, and served with shredded Cheddar cheese and sliced green onion.

title: Chicken & Corn Chowder
description: This comfort food classic is chock full of flavor and ready in 25 minutes. Cooked chicken, creamy herb and garlic soup, potatoes, corn, bacon and milk simmer together for incredible chowder that's an absolute winner!

title: Hearty Homemade Chicken Noodle Soup Express
description: There's nothing better than a good bowl of soup, like this quick-cooking and delicious chicken noodle soup, brimming with chicken, colorful vegetables and egg noodles.

title: Gumbo with Andouille Sausage
description: One taste of this fabulous gumbo and you'll think you're in New Orleans! The Cajun flavor infused broth adds incredible taste to the sausage, chicken and vegetables. Serve this at your next party for an impressive dish that's sure to be a hit with your guests!

title: Easy Chicken Chili with White Beans
description: In the mood for chili? No problem. Because you can have this flavorful chicken chili on the table in less than a half hour. It only tastes like it's been simmering all day.

title: Slow Cooker Chicken Chile Tortilla Soup
description: Spice up your day with a bowl of this warm and wonderful soup that slow cooks for hours to blend many favorite Southwestern ingredients.

title: Mexican Tortilla Soup
description: This kicked-up soup features sawtayed onions and spicy peppers combined with chicken, corn, tomatoes and black beans all simmered in a delicious broth. The result is an ultra-flavorful soup your family will love!

title: Speedy French Onion Soup
description: Warm up with a bowl of this savory soup that's loaded with incredible flavor. Caramelized onions simmer with sweet onion soup and beef consamay. It's topped with cheesy garlic Texas toast and is so good you may want to double the recipe because it will be gone in a flash!

title: Savory Vegetable Beef Soup
description: You can ladle up this flavorful, homemade beef and vegetable soup in just 30 minutes.

title: Quick & Easy Chili
description: It just doesn't get any easier or more delicious than this! Sawtayed ground beef, onion, beans and Mexican style tomato soup simmer together to make a quick and hearty chili that everyone will love.

title: Slow Cooker Jambalaya
description: This delectable, slow-cooked version of a traditional New Orleans-style dish features chicken, kielbasa and shrimp in a bed of rice that's been seasoned with Creole seasoning, green pepper, celery and diced tomato.

title: Slow Cooker Hearty Mixed Bean Stew with Sausage
description: Here's a hearty stew to feed a hungry crowd. It features a colorful array of beans simmering with sausage and chicken broth, that slow cooks for hours, leaving you free to enjoy the day.

title: Slow Cooker Hearty Beef & Bean Chili
description: Since this chili slowly simmers all day long, the flavors blend together to make each bite satisfying and delicious.

title: Quick & Easy Pumpkin Soup
description: Pumpkin, ginger, nutmeg and applesauce flavor this creamy pureayed soup that's elegant and satisfying.  Best of all, it's ready in just 45 minutes.

title: Black Bean, Corn and Turkey Chili
description: Ready in less than an hour, this satisfying twist on traditional chili tastes like it's been simmering all day!

title: Sensational Turkey Noodle Soup
description: Here is a great idea for that leftover turkey! Combine it with a few simple ingredients to make a sensational soup that's incredibly good. It's a breeze to prepare, but one taste guarantees that this will become a soup time favorite recipe.

title: Hearty Turkey Tortilla Soup
description: Leftover turkey is easily transformed into this satisfying soup with just the right amount of spice!  Ready in just 50 minutes, it's simply delish!

title: Turkey Corn Chowder
description: The subtle flavor of bacon, together with the bold taste of picante sauce, makes this quick-cooking chowder, loaded with turkey and corn, really delicious.

title: Vegetarian Chili
description: This quick-cooking stovetop chili, chock full of vegetables and two types of beans will fit the bill when you're looking for a meatless dish.

title: Wild Mushroom & White Wine Soup
description: Assorted wild mushrooms are sawtayed with garlic and shallots and then combined with white wine, creamy stock and fresh parsley. The exquisite flavor is what will have you coming back to this recipe again and again!

title: Zucchini Soup with Herbed Cream
description: It takes less than one hour to make this smooth and creamy zucchini soup, served with a dollop of flavorful herbed cream.

title: Thai Roasted Squash Soup
description: This elegant, gourmet soup features layers of flavor from unusual ingredients like cream of coconut, ginger, curry and roasted butternut squash. But what makes this soup really special is that it's incredibly simple to make.

title: West African Vegetable Stew
description: Tired of making the same old meat and potatoes stew? Here's a deliciously different vegetable stew that features an usual combination of sweet and savory ingredients that blend together beautifully with mouthwatering results.

title: Slow Cooker Chicken Tortilla Soup
description: This ultra-flavorful soup is worth the wait. The slow cooker makes it easy, and the savory combination of chicken, beans, corn and picante sauce makes it absolutely delicious!

title: Thai Chicken and Vegetable Soup
description: What makes this soup taste so good? Fresh veggies, ginger-flavored broth and coconut milk. Plus, it's ready after just 15 minutes on the stove.

title: Slow Cooker Poblano Corn Chowder with Chicken and Chorizo
description: Throw all the ingredients into the slow-cooker at once, and it will make this kicked-up corn chowder for you. Plus, the smoky chorizo and the spicy poblano chilies make this soup especially delicious.

title: Chinese Hot & Sour Soup
description: 10 minutes on the stove and you've got a restaurant-quality soup your whole family will love. The hot and sour broth is the key to the delicious bold flavor. Give it a try, you'll be so glad you did!

title: Savory Vegetable Beef Soup
description: Yum. You can ladle up this flavorful, homemade beef and vegetable soup in just 30 minutes.

title: Ham, Potato & Cabbage Soup
description: Mouthwatering, traditional flavors come together in this satisfying soup reminiscent of grandmother's kitchen.

title: Spaghetti Soup
description: This easy-to-make, heart-warming soup is as fun to eat as it is good. Try it and you'll see what we mean.

title: Taco Twist Soup
description: This family-friendly recipe mixes pasta with the great flavors of tacos to make a hearty and delicious soup.

title: Roasted Tomato & Barley Soup
description: Roasting the tomatoes, garlic and onions makes this soup especially flavorful. After the veggies are roasted, all you need is 40 minutes and you've got a robust, rustic-style soup.

title: Spicy Asian Beef & Snow Pea Soup
description: No need for takeout when you can prepare this deliciously spicy soup featuring tender-crisp vegetables and sawtayed sirloin steak strips.

title: Sausage & Spinach Soup
description: Swanson Chicken Broth is the secret to making a quick and delicious homemade soup featuring sweet Italian sausage and fresh spinach.
